{"tid":2218131,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"【爆價!!】折合約 HK$4700 - HK$6500 多款 RTX 3070 非公版歐洲網店提早上架","createTime":"2020-09-26T03:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T14:12:32.000Z","uid":202698,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"00801077d60dbf4423c72e69c5fae967978cade5","tid":2218131,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T03:54:12.000Z","msg":"【爆價!!】折合約 HK$4700 - HK$6500多款 RTX 3070 非公版歐洲網店提早上架<br />\n<br />\nNVIDIA GeForce RTX 3080、RTX 3090 系列先後在 17/9 及 24/9 日正式上市，至於中、高階玩家非常期待的 GeForce RTX 3070 就會在 10 月 15 日上市，目前 NVIDIA 官方已公佈了 GeForce RTX 3070 Founders Edition 公版會以 USD499 發售，不過香港玩家一向都只會「有得睇無得食」，都係「疊埋心水」買非公版卡啦，<span class=\"red\">最新在歐洲及英國就有網店提早放出包括 ASUS、EVGA、PALIT、PNY、INNO3D、ZOTAC 等品牌的售價，價格介乎在 519.95  - 679.90 歐元及 500 - 660 英鎊不等，折合約 HK$4,700 - HK$6,500。</span><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n根據 NVIDIA 公佈的規格，GeForce RTX 3070 將會採用 SAMSUNG 8nm 制程、GA104 繪圖核心、內建1.74億個電晶體，全新 Ampere GPU 微架構提供高達 5,888 CUDA Cores、184 Tensor Cores 及 46 個 RT Cores，核心時脈為 1.5GHz Base Clock、1.725 Boost Clock，256bit 記憶體介面但沿用 14Gbps GDDR6 記憶體顆粒，性能與 GeForce RTX 2080 Ti 相當接近。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/19792/%E7%88%86%E5%83%B9%E6%8A%98%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84_HK%244700_-_HK%246500__%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%BE_RTX_3070_%E9%9D%9E%E5%85%AC%E7%89%88%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E7%B6%B2%E5%BA%97%E6%8F%90%E6%97%A9%E4%B8%8A%E6%9E%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F19792%2F%25E7%2588%2586%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%258A%2598%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%25B4%2584_HK%25244700_-_HK%25246500__%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25AC%25BE_RTX_3070_%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%2589%2588%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%25BA%2597%25E6%258F%2590%25E6%2597%25A9%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259E%25B6&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=88c8034d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/19792/%E7%88%86%E5%83%B9%E6%8A%98%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84_HK%244700_-_HK%246500__%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%BE_RTX_3070_%E9%9D%9E%E5%85%AC%E7%89%88%E6%AD%